27une dame de l\u0027ancien temps, en robe de brocart dor\u00e9 \u00e0 revers d\u0027hermine, tenant un faucon blanc sur sa main droite gant\u00e9e et un coeur dans la main gauche. La figure se d\u00e9tache sur un fond gris. L\u0027accoutrement \u00e0 la fois bizarre et luxueux du personnage, surcharg\u00e9 de bijoux, indique clairement qu\u0027il s\u0027agit d\u0027un portrait imaginaire visant \u00e0 repr\u00e9senter une grande dame d\u0027une ancienne lign\u00e9e et d\u0027une \u00e9poque lointaine, probablement li\u00e9e \u00e0 l\u0027histoire des Pays-Bas, dont il n\u0027existait pas d\u0027effigie de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence.","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Paul Delaroche ; vente, Paris, 15-17 juin 1857, no 44 - Charles Sauvageot (1781-1860) ; don en 1860.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Derni\u00e8re provenance : Sauvageot, Paul","note":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"startYear":1860,"endYear":null}]}],"ownedBy":"","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"collection":[{"value":"Sauvageot, Paul"},{"value":"Delaroche, Paul"}],"place":[{"value":"Paris, Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, oeuvre en rapport"}],"subject":[{"value":"portrait"},{"value":"Animal, faucon"}],"technic":[{"value":"encre noire \u00e0 la plume"},{"value":"parchemin"},{"value":"rehauts d\u0027or"},{"value":"enluminure"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/11\/14\/87\/00\/AGO111487-000_PE.jpg","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/11\/14\/87\/00\/AGO111487-000_PE.jpg","copyright":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, dist. GrandPalaisRmn \/ Martine Beck-Coppola","type":"","position":0}]}